SIpFb.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/b7/31/64544_SIpFb.jpg"},"summary":"        秋叶纷飞的港口小镇，一只孤独的企鹅彷徨在空荡荡的街道上。它饥肠辘辘，无所依靠，漫无目的来到了一个小男孩的家中。企鹅似乎对男孩的收音机颇感兴趣，男孩则有些不知所措，只得把它送到失物招领处，然而根本没人丢失过企鹅。小企鹅成为男孩的累赘，几番周折，男孩得知企鹅都是生长在南极。于是，他制作了小木船，和小企鹅踏上了前往南极的归乡旅途……\r\n　　本片由英国著名动画工作室AKA根据绘本名家奥利弗·杰法（Oliver Jeffer）的同名原著改编，制成后于圣诞节之时在英国第4频道播放。该片荣获2009年英国电影电视艺术学院儿童奖最佳影片奖和2009年芝加哥国际儿童电影节儿童评委会奖最佳动画片。","name":"Lost and Found","name_cn":"远在天边","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2008","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画短片","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈系","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"企鹅","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2008年","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童话","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"回家","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JimBroadbent","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OliverJeffers","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"3D","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Philip_Hunt","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"菲利普·亨特","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PhilipHunt","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AM","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧洲","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"绘本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"定格动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7.5★","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"远在天边"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"真我之旅"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"2008-12-24(英国)"},{"key":"片长","value":"24分钟"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.studioaka.co.uk/go/lostandfound"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"导演","value":"Philip Hunt"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":44,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":3,"5":2,"6":9,"7":12,"8":